# Narrow allowlist for git-shield false positives in this repo.
# One regex per line. See https://github.com/vekexasia/git-shield#allowlist

# ── Public URLs that aren't PII ──
^https?://(www\.)?keepachangelog\.com(/.*)?$
^https?://(www\.)?nextjs\.org(/.*)?$
^https?://github\.com/vekexasia/risto-menu(/.*)?$

# ── Drizzle snapshot identifiers ──
# drizzle generates a fresh UUID for each migration snapshot's `id`/`prevId`.
# These appear in backend/drizzle/meta/*_snapshot.json and are not secrets.
^[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{12}$

# ── Italian food / menu vocabulary in test fixtures + demo seed ──
# Dish, course, and translation names that the PII scanner mistakes for personal names.
(?i)^pizza\s+margherita$
(?i)^margherita$
(?i)^tiramis[uù]$
(?i)^cucina$
(?i)^antipasti$
(?i)^primi$
(?i)^secondi$
(?i)^dolci$
(?i)^bevande$
(?i)^vorspeisen$
(?i)^entr[ée]es$
(?i)^speisekarte$
(?i)^bruschetta$
(?i)^carpaccio$
(?i)^burrata$
(?i)^ravioli$
(?i)^spaghetti$
(?i)^branzino$
(?i)^tagliata$
(?i)^prosecco$
(?i)^merlot$
(?i)^carbonara$
